打开CMD,进入Tomcat bin目录

Microsoft Windows [版本 6.1.7601]
版权所有 (c) 2009 Microsoft Corporation。保留所有权利。

C:\Users\Administrator>D:

D:\>cd D:\scanServer\apache-tomcat-8.0.26-8000\apache-tomcat-8.0.26\bin

D:\scanServer\apache-tomcat-8.0.26-8000\apache-tomcat-8.0.26\bin>service install
 SmartPRO_8000_BGB
